  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As the Apostle says ( Hebrews 6:16 ), oaths are taken for the purpose of confirmation. Now speculative propositions receive confirmation from reason, which proceeds from principles known naturally and infallibly true . But particular contingent</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
