  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q098.a002.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">either that God ignores the truth or that He is willing to bear witness to a falsehood. Therefore perjury is manifestly a sin opposed to religion, to which it belongs to show reverence to God .</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
