  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">ng to Psalm 115:12 , "What shall I render to the Lord for all the things that He hath rendered to me?" On this respect "religion" is annexed to justice since, according to Tully (De invent. ii, 53), it consists in offering service and ceremonial rites or worship to "some superior nature</data>
