  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a014.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">We may speak about prayer in two ways: first, by considering it in itself; secondly, by considering it in its cause . The cause of prayer is the desire of charity , from which prayer ought to arise: and this desire ought</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
