  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a015.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 13 ) prayer , besides causing spiritual consolation at the time of praying , has a twofold efficacy in respect of a future effect, namely, efficacy in meriting and efficacy in impetrating. Now p</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
