  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a003.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">l those things through which reverence is shown to God , belong to religion. Now man shows reverence to God by means of prayer , in so far as he subjects himself to Him, and by praying confesses that he needs Him as the Author of his goods. Hence it is evident that prayer is properly a</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
