  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a004.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">Prayer is offered to a person in two ways: first, as to be fulfilled by him, secondly, as to be obtained through him. On the first way we offer prayer to God alone, s</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
