  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">and besides to offer to the Lord things appertaining to the people, their prayers , for instance, their sacrifices and oblations. Thus the Apostle says ( Hebrews 5:1 ): "Every high priest taken from among men is ordained for men in the things that appertain to God , that he may offer up</data>
