  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q088.a004.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( 1 and 2 ), a vow is a promise made to God . Now one makes a promise to a man under one aspect, and to God under another. Because we promise something to a man for his own profit; since it profits him th</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
