  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q088.a008.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 1 ), a vow is a promise made to God . Now no man can firmly bind himself by a promise to do what is in another's power, but only to that which is entirely in his own power. Now whoever is subjec</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
