  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As may be gathered from what has been said above ( Article 7 ), vows are of two kinds, simple and solemn . And since, as stated in the same article, the solemnization of a vow consists in a spiritual blessing and consecr</data>
