  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above, sins against religion consist in going beyond the mean of virtue in respect of certain circumstances ( Article 1 ). For as we have stated ( I-II:72:9 ), not every diversity of corrupt circumstances diffe</data>
