  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q095.a004.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">All divination by invoking demons is unlawful for two reasons. The first is gathered from the principle of divination , which is a compact made expressly with a demon by the very fact of invoking him. This is altogether </data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
