  <data key="d17">As stated above ( 1 and 2 ), the operation of the demon thrusts itself into those divinations which are based on false and vain opinions, in order that man's mind may become entangled in vanity and falsehood. Now one mak</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
