  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( II-II:81:5 ; I-II:101:4 ), a thing is called "sacred" through being deputed to the divine worship. Now just as a thing acquires an aspect of good through being deputed to a good end, so does a thing ass</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
