  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q099.a002.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">Wherever we find a special aspect of deformity, there must needs be a special sin ; because the species of a thing is derived chiefly from its formal aspect, and not from its matter or subject. Now in sacrilege we find a</data>
