  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 1 ), the sin of sacrilege consists in the irreverent treatment of a sacred thing. Now reverence is due to a sacred thing by reason of its holiness : and consequently the species of sacrilege mus</data>
