  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">In the award of punishments two points must be considered. First equality, in order that the punishment may be just , and that "by what things a man sinneth by the same . . . he may be tormented" ( Wisdom 11:17 ). On thi</data>
