  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">; because the species of a thing is derived chiefly from its formal aspect, and not from its matter or subject. Now in sacrilege we find a special aspect of deformity, namely, the violation of a sacred thing by treating it irreverently. Hence it is a special sin . Moreover, it is opposed</data>
