  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( I-II:18:2 ) an act is evil generically when it bears on undue matter . Now a spiritual thing is undue matter for buying and selling for three reasons. First, because a spiritual thing cannot be appraised at any earthly price, even as it is sa</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
